Package com.aseproject.facebook

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseListElement
    Base class for a list element in the App main display, consisting of an icon to the left, and a two line display to the right.
    FbShare
    This Activity creates a listView with its sublist views and allows sharing on facebook.
    FullListView
    A subclass of ListView that will always show the full list of elements.
    PickerActivity
    This Activity class enhances the Friend or Place Picker(fb sdk) by adding a title and a confirmation button.
